<note n="0762007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0762007">辯＝辨【明】</note>
<note n="0762008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0762008">（謂）＋諸【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0762009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0762009">入＝八【明】</note>
<note n="0763001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0763001">串＝慣【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0764001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0764001">〔無〕－【聖】</note>
<note n="0764002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0764002">切＝初【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0764003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0764003">攝＝擇【聖】</note>
<note n="0765001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0765001">客非主＝容非立【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0765002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0765002">減＝滅【聖】</note>
<note n="0766001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0766001">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
